Lastly there are many invited in India free.

01:44:46.482 --> 01:44:51.469
Most of them may not also pay,

01:44:51.493 --> 01:44:55.981
those who cannot pay for travel should let us know.

01:45:23.380 --> 01:45:27.205
No no, we have invited many people to India.

01:45:27.261 --> 01:45:35.232
They should give their names and
those who are free for Ganapatipule

01:45:35.257 --> 01:45:38.450
but who have paid for the travelling

01:45:38.468 --> 01:45:42.925
and those who have not paid for travelling also should give their names.

01:46:24.765 --> 01:46:32.389
Also some of the letters who cannot paid are invited.

01:46:50.553 --> 01:46:52.354
May God bless you all.
